{"tid":1761730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實嗰啲乜撚嘢和你lunch有咩用？","createTime":"2019-11-29T06:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T06:52:25.000Z","uid":240250,"like":23,"dislike":248,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"5d942933f3867e99deb7d74f8c0423e4ef637f70","tid":1761730,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"中環， 九龍灣， 觀塘班和理非真係好撚勁， 日日和你lunch<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1760207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1760207</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n即係呢啲咁嘅gap野，我唔喺嗰頭返工真係撚知你咩事咩，搞左幾多日話？我今日見到上面個post先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞埋哂呢啲廢野邊有noise架，慳返啖氣啦！"},{"pid":"7de55d880050c4b944dc7f4dc0165dac3ba1e4a0","tid":1761730,"uid":198590,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:03:49.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#240250 - 徐永強</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span>, 請大家多加注意, 善用不推文回覆！<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>我正式宣布，大家休息至立法會選舉！！！ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>前線手足嘅血汗總算有回報，大家記住沉著冷靜，唔好再開花，免得令民意逆轉！記住血債票償呀！要喺體制內打贏佢哋！<br />\n嚟！一齊叫！光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1756452/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1756452/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>香港人終於贏左第一仗！多謝勇武手足，你地終於可以退下火線 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>首先多謝各位前線勇武手足，你地嘅血汗已經化為選票，我哋幫你報咗仇。<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fhoho.gif&h=26011529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區選大勝，證明民意喺我哋呢邊，我哋下一步就係要建立黃色經濟圈，<br />\n等啲黃店發大嚟搞，請返留咗案底嘅手足，再下一步就係贏埋立法會選舉。<br />\n現階段抗爭運動正式轉形，最緊要唔好再搞以下幾樣野，<br />\n因為太影響民生或者畫面唔好睇，有可能會令民意反彈：<br />\n1. 堵路<br />\n2. 火魔<br />\n3. 裝修<br />\n4. 神獸<br />\n5. 黎明行動<br />\n6. 三罷<br />\n想繼續表達訴求嘅可以考慮星期日搞下遊行集會（記得要有不反），<br />\n記住唔好影響市民，唔好失民意，最好做咗都冇人知！<br />\nCome on！光復香港！時代革命！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" />[img]<a href=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gi&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=993aa9dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi</a></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1755038/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1755038/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>運動已完，大家請接受現實 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>打左幾個月而家先返轉頭玩和理非玩感化，一定冇noise。林鄭嘅策略簡單暴力，但非常成功地將前線拉得七七八八，剩返嗰班和理非不足為患（其實對家由頭到尾都冇放和理非在眼內），就由得你喺度圍爐打飛機，打多排冇癮就自己散。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1743386/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1743386/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>請立即停止黎明行動！ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>黎明左咁多日，打工仔都適應哂，要返工嘅早兩個鐘出門口爬山都會返工，最多係遲一兩個鐘，但再搞落去只會令打工仔屌聲四起，增加民鬥民嘅情況。我呼籲大家立即停止黎明行動，準時返工返學方為上策。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1740561/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1740561/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>正式宣布黎明行動唔撚使再搞 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>好簡單既道理：一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭。<br />\n所有招數都係用一次，唔食住上星期個勢搞落去就唔使旨意再搞，你不妨睇下呢場運動有咩招數係停完之後再攞返出黎用係work既？<br />\n所以各位準時返工啦<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fsmile.gif&h=d434394b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1737015/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1737015/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a>"},{"pid":"1349f9b67755186196df0589aafc238ad26a6e5f","tid":1761730,"uid":94465,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"人地鍾意和你lunch關你鬼事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉"},{"pid":"f5b0198ff75efd92b8ae2aba609c8ee868aa9d26","tid":1761730,"uid":125925,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:05:17.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"3a12418e709dbab58af83096aae7d95b67482707","tid":1761730,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:05:32.000Z","msg":"和你唱會有用D，士氣好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004c058c2b094c68133e7564afc8e07bcca30982","tid":1761730,"uid":239663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"cbf04536314196b5a92cc7375163feda59ea1be8","tid":1761730,"uid":98317,"like":4,"dislike":24,"score":-20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:06:00.000Z","msg":"其實真係冇用.....政府係當我地係小丑咁睇，你地話我係五毛都係咁講，對成件有幫助"},{"pid":"db5485dfbec8cd98e854b552285b075443bab51a","tid":1